snippet.title: Stickin' The Landing - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Puzzles and stickers enthusiasts, come closer!

The #StickinTheLanding Demo is now available on Steam! It's free, it's full of content, it's beautiful and... did we mention it's free?

Try it out, tell us what you think, pick a sticky and send it to the person you like!

Get it now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2740260/Stickin_the_Landing/
